---
// src/components/AuthorProfile.astro
---
<section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="avatar-container" id="author-avatar-btn" title="点击查看关于我">
            <img src="/avatar.jpg" alt="OKay" class="hero-avatar interactive-avatar">
            <div class="avatar-hover-hint">关于我</div>
        </div>
        <h1>Hi，我是 <span class="text-accent">OKay</span> 👋</h1>
        <p class="hero-desc">嵌入式 Linux AI 开发者 · 专注瑞芯微全系列芯片<br>高速PCB硬件开发 & Linux驱动开发</p>
        <div class="hero-tags">
            <span>RK3588</span><span>RK3568</span><span>RK3566</span><span>RK3399</span><span>RK3328</span><span>RKNN</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Author Intro Modal -->
<div class="author-modal-overlay" id="author-modal">
    <div class="author-modal-content">
        <button class="modal-close-btn" id="modal-close-btn">
            <span class="material-icons-round">close</span>
        </button>
        <div class="modal-header">
            <img src="/avatar.jpg" alt="OKay" class="modal-avatar">
            <h2>OKay</h2>
            <p class="modal-subtitle">嵌入式全栈开发者 / 硬件极客</p>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
            <p>你好！我是 OKay，一名热爱在原子世界与比特世界之间搭建桥梁的工程师。</p>
            <p>我专注于**瑞芯微（Rockchip）**全系列处理器的开发，涉及领域包括：</p>
            <ul>
                <li>⚡ <strong>高速硬件流片：</strong> 从原理图设计到多层盲埋孔 PCB 叠层阻抗控制。</li>
                <li>🐧 <strong>底层驱动移植：</strong> U-Boot、Linux Kernel 裁剪、设备树编写与外设驱动。</li>
                <li>🧠 <strong>边缘 AI 部署：</strong> 基于 RKNN、TensorRT 的高帧率机器视觉落地应用。</li>
            </ul>
            <p>在这里，我会把踩过的坑、总结的经验毫无保留地分享出来。希望能在这个开源的世界里，与你一起探索技术的无限可能！</p>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer">
            <a href="https://github.com/OKayJH" target="_blank" class="modal-social-link">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 19c-5 1.5-5-2.5-7-3m14 6v-3.87a3.37 3.37 0 0 0-.94-2.61c3.14-.35 6.44-1.54 6.44-7A5.44 5.44 0 0 0 20 4.77 5.07 5.07 0 0 0 19.91 1S18.73.65 16 2.48a13.38 13.38 0 0 0-7 0C6.27.65 5.09 1 5.09 1A5.07 5.07 0 0 0 5 4.77a5.44 5.44 0 0 0-1.5 3.78c0 5.42 3.3 6.61 6.44 7A3.37 3.37 0 0 0 9 18.13V22"></path></svg>
                GitHub
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .avatar-container {
        position: relative;
        display: inline-block;
        cursor: pointer;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .interactive-avatar {
        transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275), box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .avatar-container:hover .interactive-avatar {
        transform: scale(1.05);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.3);
    }
    .avatar-hover-hint {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: -10px;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        background: var(--text-main);
        color: var(--bg-main);
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        padding: 4px 8px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        opacity: 0;
        transition: opacity 0.3s ease, bottom 0.3s ease;
        pointer-events: none;
        white-space: nowrap;
        font-weight: 600;
    }
    .avatar-container:hover .avatar-hover-hint {
        opacity: 1;
        bottom: -5px;
    }

    /* Modal Styles */
    .author-modal-overlay {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100vw;
        height: 100vh;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
        backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        z-index: 1000;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        opacity: 0;
        visibility: hidden;
        transition: opacity 0.3s ease, visibility 0.3s ease;
    }
    .author-modal-overlay.active {
        opacity: 1;
        visibility: visible;
    }
    .author-modal-content {
        background: var(--bg-secondary);
        width: 90%;
        max-width: 500px;
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 40px;
        position: relative;
        transform: translateY(30px) scale(0.95);
        transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    }
    .author-modal-overlay.active .author-modal-content {
        transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
    }
    .modal-close-btn {
        position: absolute;
        top: 20px;
        right: 20px;
        background: var(--bg-tertiary);
        border: none;
        width: 36px;
        height: 36px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        cursor: pointer;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }
    .modal-close-btn:hover {
        background: var(--bg-hover);
        color: var(--text-main);
        transform: rotate(90deg);
    }
    .modal-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .modal-avatar {
        width: 80px;
        height: 80px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        object-fit: cover;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        border: 3px solid var(--border-light);
    }
    .modal-header h2 {
        margin: 0 0 4px 0;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    .modal-subtitle {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--accent);
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    .modal-body {
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .modal-body p {
        margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .modal-body ul {
        margin: 0 0 16px 0;
        padding-left: 20px;
    }
    .modal-body li {
        margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .modal-body strong {
        color: var(--text-main);
    }
    .modal-footer {
        margin-top: 32px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border-light);
        padding-top: 24px;
    }
    .modal-social-link {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        background: var(--bg-main);
        color: var(--text-main);
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        transition: all 0.2s ease;
        border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    }
    .modal-social-link:hover {
        border-color: var(--accent);
        color: var(--accent);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
</style>

<script is:inline>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
        const avatarBtn = document.getElementById('author-avatar-btn');
        const modal = document.getElementById('author-modal');
        const closeBtn = document.getElementById('modal-close-btn');

        if(avatarBtn && modal && closeBtn) {
            // Open modal
            avatarBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
                modal.classList.add('active');
                document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden'; // Prevent background scrolling
            });

            // Close modal via button
            closeBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
                modal.classList.remove('active');
                document.body.style.overflow = '';
            });

            // Close modal via overlay click
            modal.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
                if (e.target === modal) {
                    modal.classList.remove('active');
                    document.body.style.overflow = '';
                }
            });
            
            // Close via Escape key
            document.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
                if(e.key === 'Escape' && modal.classList.contains('active')) {
                    modal.classList.remove('active');
                    document.body.style.overflow = '';
                }
            });
        }
    });
</script>
